SUMMARY:Data Lancaster Coffee Meetup
DESCRIPTION:Data Lancaster\n**Don't miss the final Data Lancaster Coffee M
 eetup of the year!**\n\nWe meet up at the Mean Cup coffee shop and chat ab
 out whatever topics come to mind. Attendees tend to work in data-related j
 obs\, so expect at least some data-related discussions\, and attendees sha
 ring what they've been up to on the data-related projects they're working 
 on is common.\n\nBe sure to join the Data Lancaster Meetup group in order 
 to receive notifications about next year's events!\n\n*(And if you have a 
 conflict this month and want to plan for the future\, we meet the third Fr
 iday of the month every month except November and December)*
